ent-RMCCarPileup = burned out vehicle pileup
    .desc = Burned-out vehicles block your path, their charred frames and shattered glass hinting at recent chaos. The acrid smell of smoke lingers.

ent-RMCPropVehicleMonoSupronBlack = Mono-Supron
    .desc = The 'Mono-Supron', a mass-produced civilian vehicle for the colonial markets, in and outside of the United Nations. Produced by 'Mizutani' a car marque and associated operating division of the Weston-Yamada Corporation.
